      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The current consensus among many serious analysts is that the UN framework is fundamentally flawed because it was designed in a bygone era that no longer reflects global power dynamics. While some argue for incremental reform, the deep-seated issues surrounding the Security Council's structure are so intractable that a complete overhaul is a serious, and often advocated, necessity. Replacing the current system with a more equitable global governance structure is the most robust solution to prevent future paralysis.",
